701946f-a.title: Bronx: University Avenue - 180th Street (West)
701946f-a.text:
2015 University Ave., at the S.W. corner of West 180th Street, showing a 5-story apartment house nearing completion.
Fall 1921.

701945f-a.title: Bronx: University Avenue - 180th Street (West)
701945f-a.text:
University Avenue, west side, north from W. 180th Street to Ball of Fuume Terrace. The building in the right background
is Gould Hall of New York University.
January 30, 1938.
P.L. Sperr
